data.text:
On December 22, 2016 James Vincent McNulty Sr.; Beloved husband of 62 years to Loretta McNulty (Nee Fisher); Loving father of John McNulty, Judy Simon (Nee McNulty) and her husband Gregg and the late Boh McNulty; Cherished grandfather of Richard Simon and his wife the late Sandra, Amy Purvis (Nee Simon) and her husband Tom and Kellie Simon; Dear great grandfather of Vicki Simon, Zoey Purvis and Colton Purvis.

A graveside service will be held December 27th at 2 pm in Holly Hill Memorial Gardens Cemetery 10201 Bird River Road Middle River, Maryland 21220.
